Role of QA in SDLC
## Requirement gathering and analysis
 QA role:
- Participate in requirement review meetings
- Ensure requirements are clear,complete , testable and traceable
- Help write acceptence criteria

##Development
  QA role:
-Collaborate Closely with Developers
-Write detailed test cases,test scenarios and test data

## Testing
QA roles:
-Execute Test Cases
-User acceptence testing support
-log defects and verify fixes

##Deployment
QA roles:
-Perform Smoke/sanity test.
-Support Release team with test execution or documentation

